  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to

      1- detect and quantify HCV-PI resistant mutants with ultra-deep pyrosequencing (UDPS)
      technology, 2 - detect SNPs in P-glyocoprotein and CYP3A genes, in HCV mono-infected patients
      under/after Telaprevir treatment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
